All fights and battles are taken as quite a different game - beloved by many casual fun with a square field and the colored balloons, which are necessary \&quot;kick\&quot; from the field in a certain sequence. But many of the familiar rules of the game enhanced with new, unprecedented opportunities. For the plain colored balls hidden army and magic, players come to the aid of spells and artifacts, the hero gains experience and new abilities ...

The result was a unique blend of puzzle and role-playing game complete. Crossing two dissimilar genres gave a stunning result: the game was recognized as one of the best casual entertainment in recent years by most gaming publications and has earned numerous awards. In a world of fun at the office Puzzle Quest is no competition.

Features:
The perfect combination of puzzle, RPG and turn based strategy!;
An epic story based on the universe Warlords!;
Fascinating battle!;
A lot of opponents, each with its own twist!;
Four types of magic!.

Puzzle Quest: Galactrix

Continued excellent game that combines elements of RPG and logic puzzle. In place of fantasy sketches come a science fiction story. The plot, in fact, explode in the direction of an unknown alien race, eager to destroy humanity. The player also will serve as the fighting against the invaders combat pilot, skillfully maneuvering between factions and alliances. This means that the focus on diplomacy, trade and construction of ships have many times more. Plus, the battle Puzzle Quest: Galactrix will now develop on a hexagonal grid.

Features:
Create a strong pilot, who gets the skills and ships as the battle;
Look for new items to make the ship and the pilot\'s all-powerful;
Trade in goods across the galaxy to increase the wealth;
Each enemy requires different tactics;
Present regime, \&quot;the galaxy\&quot;.

Puzzle Quest 2

Puzzle Quest 2 will take us to the fantasy world, where there is always a powerful evil that has overcome the main character. This time the evil was placed in the village of Verloren - and its need to save. Vacant position of the protagonist can take one of the four available characters - the magician, the Inquisitor, a barbarian and assassins. Each of them has its own set of skills and unique abilities that can be pumped by spending experience earned in battle. A battle then take the form of cute puzzles where you need to quickly and cleverly combine the same elements pazzlovye appearing on the screen, to build a chain of them and literally force your mind to destroy the enemy.

Features:
The gameplay, as well as in the first game based on the match-3 puzzle game with role-playing elements. In the story, the player must protect a village from Verloren zlovogo demon Gorgon. In olitiche from moving on a schematic map of the global, as in the first game, Puzzle Quest 2 is now an isometric view and the gameplay is based on a study of caves near the village;
The game is available four character classes: Sorcerer, Templar, Barbarian, and Assassin.





